faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n永遠唔會改進"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T04:09:26.000Z","msg":"因為中國人嘅思想仲停留係百幾年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4bcead28d481662fd8197295c8b24f148972b6","tid":1951444,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T04:10:26.000Z","msg":"戰鬥打響後，慈禧先將義和團送上前線當炮灰，然後灰溜溜地帶著光緒逃跑到西安，北京被八國聯軍攻陷。我們知道，八國聯軍進京後燒殺搶掠，無惡不作，搶走我大中華無數珍寶。不過，在他們踏進北京之初，卻被眼前的景象給嚇了一大跳。<br />\n<br />\n原來，當時的北京城，大多數人家的家中都沒有廁所，街上也無公廁。因此男人要大小便，一般都到街上解決，只要別在集市或者大馬路中央就行。而女人則在家中用便桶解決，攢夠了再倒到外面，以至於北京城滿街屎尿。<br />\n<br />\n周街屙屎屙撚咗幾多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a8ef9c3c8a2da3773801419d11bd3b0178e4fd","tid":1951444,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T04:20:27.000Z","msg":"死都拗返生(嗌交部)"},{"pid":"0f663c75c09ffc2bd9f0f3fe3e5637e2a6e438cb","tid":1951444,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"56a8ef9c3c8a2da3773801419d11bd3b0178e4fd","tid":1951444,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T04:20:27.000Z","msg":"死都拗返生(嗌交部)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T04:39:30.000Z","msg":"老屈 推個病毒來源比人就係最厲害了 我的來源國  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}